{
  "stem": "7358.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Apparently we were not the only ones that hiding places.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So the-- the Ukrainian and the Germans were-- were going through the houses and looking for fake ceilings and extra-- looking for hiding places.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And every time they discovered one, they would take the people out and shoot them right in front of their homes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So we-- we knew that this was really the final-- the final solution.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we were so petrified, we didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And during the day, the Germans used to-- they came and-- the Ukrainians mostly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were-- they were-- they are the police, and they used to be supervised by some German officers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But the job was mostly done by the Ukrainian police.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they used to come into the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And from time to time, they would hammer on the floors with-- with the butts of their rifles to see if there's hollow-- hollow space.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But since our basement was in a little room outside of the house, we were never discovered.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And with us were-- were also two babies that belonged to two-- to two of the women.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And-- and the babies cried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They wanted food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And every time is so happened-- It looked like every time there was a critical moment when people came to-- to search the house or look, they started to cry.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And-- and the men subsequently put pillows on top of the babies, and the babies were suffocated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And one of the mothers, I remember, became so hysterical that she had to be subdued by-- by-- by the-- by some of the men.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a big tragedy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were sitting in that-- in this little basement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were two dead babies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And our life wasn't-- wasn't worth anything neither.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
